In the MATTER OF Brian MCDEVITT, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 037281989) D-51 September Term 2018
082143 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 6, 2018

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented, it is ORDERED that Brian McDevitt of Norristown, Pennsylvania, who was admitted to the bar of this State in 1989, and who was suspended from the practice of law for a period of six months, effective November 30, 2017, by Order of this Court filed November 1, 2017, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
